Mondi Says That First-Half Profit Was ‘Considerably Higher’ Than Year Ago

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-07-22T06:14:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-22/mondi-says-that-first-half-profit-was-considerably-higher-than-year-ago.html
Mondi Plc said “underlying
operating profit” for the first half of this year was
“considerably higher” than the year earlier.  Earnings per share are between 38 and 43 euro cents, it
said today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
